üö® SATURN HAS 146 MOONS MORE THAN ANY OTHER PLANET IN OUR SOLAR SYSTEM 

Saturn has 146 moons, the most of any planet, with sizes ranging from larger than Mercury (Titan) to as small as a sports arena. 

Enceladus, one of its smaller moons, has a global ocean beneath an icy shell. 

These moons influence Saturn's rings and magnetosphere and are key targets for future deep space missions. 

Some were discovered by notable astronomers like G.D. Cassini and W. Herschel, and many are recognized by the International Astronomical Union (IAU).

Source: NASA
Media Source: @latestinspace

I‚Äôm 100% in support of adults pursuing whatever gender they please, by whatever means they like. 

More power to you! 

However, we will look back at this time, when doctors and ‚Äúprofessionals‚Äù pressured parents to perform surgery and give hormones to *children*, with great shame and regret.  

The detransition stories are just starting, and they are devastating. 

These stories always include the parents and children being bullied into making irreversible decisions.

They make decisions they don‚Äôt fully understand but are told will solve a complex problem. However, in most cases, this ‚Äúproblem‚Äù is solved best with love, compassion, counseling, and time. 

Adolescence is challenging 100% of the time, as we all have experienced. 

Imagine your darkest and most confusing moment as a teenager. Now, imagine a group of authorities telling you that your gender confusion causes all your pain and that you can solve all of that pain with surgery and hormones. 

Now imagine the state of California acting to hide this child‚Äôs struggle from their parents ‚Äî and then pursuing a gender transition covertly with the child. 

That is the crime that is happening right now. 

We don‚Äôt let kids smoke vapes or drink until they are fully informed of the ramifications of those decisions as adults  ‚Äî yet we put them on puberty blockers and have them do surgery to change their gender as teenagers? 

What is the rush? 

There isn‚Äôt one, so they tell the parents, ‚ÄúYour child will kill themselves if they don‚Äôt transition.‚Äù

This is pure evil. 

There are no parents who agree with this, there are only bullied and confused parents‚Ä¶ and that needs to end now. 

I say this with unlimited compassion and love for any child or family dealing with gender dysphoria. 

Please speak up parents.
